OL,5,G0800 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,6,     FWe meet again with series
OL,7,     Ffavourites Bambi and Johnny.
OL,8,     FThey've been busy since we last
OL,9,     Fmet them with a move along the
OL,10,     FMediterranean to the beautiful,
OL,11,     Fquiet coastal town of Huelva.
OL,12,G0900 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,13,     FWe meet Johnny Diamond, who, as
OL,14,     Fhis name suggests, is an absolute
OL,15,     Fgeezer and prides himself on
OL,16,     Fhaving more front than Brighton.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
