OL,5,G1400 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FIt is Vicky's first pursuit, and
OL,7,     Fit doesn't disappoint. After a
OL,8,     Frace through Bradford, an Audi
OL,9,     Fslams into a parked car. The
OL,10,     Fdriver runs, but the car he
OL,11,     Fcrashed into has a secret.
OL,12,G1500 Police Interceptors
OL,13,     FIt takes a stinger operation to
OL,14,     Fstop a dangerous driver who
OL,15,     Freverse-rammed the cops, but the
OL,16,     Finterceptors are in for a surprise
OL,17,     Fwhen they see who is behind the
OL,18,     Fwheel.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
