OL,5,G1830 Home and Away
OL,6,     FLacey lashes out. Richie feels the
OL,7,     Fweight of his actions. Cash takes
OL,8,     Fthe high road.
OL,9,G1900 GPs: Behind Closed Doors
OL,10,     FIn a custom-built mobile surgery,
OL,11,     FGPs have a busy week helping
OL,12,     Fpatients including a boy with an
OL,13,     Finverted chest, a woman with a
OL,14,     Fmysterious rash, and an injury
OL,15,     Fcaused by a horse.
OL,16,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,17,     FThe staff and patients of
OL,18,     FBarnsley's A&E department are put
OL,19,     Funder the microscope. The hospital
OL,20,     Fis two porters down, marking a big
OL,21,     Fproblem for Sister Jane.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
